{"tid":1426034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金融業是香港經濟的四大主要行業之一","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:23:32.000Z","uid":10503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de34b8d2b2c0a33484469ac6dd36caa6cadac812","tid":1426034,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"擠兌（也稱為擠提；兌是兌現，提則是指提款）指的是銀行或金融機構被大批的存款客戶要求提款領回自有的儲金，通常發生在銀行的營運上有重大負面傳聞之時，銀行遭遇集中且密集的提款，很可能支應不及而宣告營運困難，倘若未得到其他援助或讓擠兌情事減緩，則該銀行極有可能因此宣告倒閉以及信用破產。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>千祈唔好咁做呀<br />\n咁樣會影響到銀行正常運作架<br />\n會好影響到市民架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"f4becf172a966ad012c829e19825a5e649b85c2e","tid":1426034,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/082201_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F082201_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=13925023&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/082206_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F082206_2977afc1b097d20f61aa68323012b6ed.png&h=8a236def&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/082207_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F082207_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=55cf3034&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/082210_aadf05